# Bookworm Trait Template
# For Sims who love reading and learning

Bookworm Trait
  description: "This Sim loves reading and gets lost in books"
  category: lifestyle
  rarity: common
  benefits:
    - faster reading speed
    - mood boost from reading
    - knowledge gain

