Read Book
  description: "Get lost in an engaging book"
  type: object
  duration: 90
  tests:
    - actor has bookworm trait
    - book is available
    - actor is in quiet location
    - actor is not interrupted
  effects:
    - increase mood by 30
    - increase knowledge skill by 2
    - add focused feeling
    - add relaxed feeling

